<title>Rate a song</title>
  
  <p>The easiest way to rate a song in <app>Rhythmbox</app> is the make the 
  <gui>Ratings</gui> feature visible in the main window.</p>
  
  <p>To make <em>Ratings</em> visible in the <app>Rhythmbox</app> interface,
  select <guiseq><gui>Edit</gui><gui>Preferences</gui></guiseq>. In the 
  <gui>Visible Columns</gui> portion of the <gui>General</gui> tab, check the
  box for <gui>Rating</gui>.</p>

